data.description: Price reduced to $205,000! Take a look at this spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in beautiful Elbow Lake! This classic home features two main floor living/family rooms. The large, 17 x 23 family room, is great for all your entertainment needs and movie nights. All Kitchen appliances are included. The formal dining room has a full glass door to the back yard that brings in a lot of natural light. The open staircase will lead you upstairs to 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. You’ll love the space and convenience of the master ensuite. It features a walk in closet with washer and dryer included, and beautiful private bathroom. The basement has recently been done by Innovative Basements and includes a transferable lifetime warranty. This home has central air, vinyl siding, and a great enclosed privacy fence around the entire backyard. Inside and out, this home has great space for you to live life to its fullest!
